cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.CL 

This paper deals with the task of semantic segmentation, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also extensively uses deep learning techniques, which falls under the subfield of machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper introduces a novel approach to incorporating high-level constraints using a Restricted Boltzmann Machine, which falls under the subfield of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also evaluates its approach on datasets related to face labelling (cs.MM) and pedestrian parsing (cs.CL).
